"},{"content":"Add cashews, coconut milk, curry powder, salt, pepper and reserved chilli mixture and blend <b>1 min\/speed 9<b>."},{"content":"Add zucchini, pumpkin, tomatoes and spring onions\/shallots and mix <b>30 sec\/\/speed 2<b>. Divide between bowls with cauliflower rice and garnish with coriander leaves to serve."}],"hintsAndTricks":["You can replace the fresh turmeric with ½ tsp ground turmeric in this recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","25m","4 portions"]}